data.description: Dive into a rewarding project with 414 Douglas, a genuine fixer-upper gem. This home boasts an open living room and kitchen layout, waiting for your unique touch. Located in a region rich with growth opportunities, this property serves as a blank slate, perfect for investors or homeowners with a vision. Embrace the potential and craft a space tailored to your design aspirations at 414 Douglas
